LITH ire - leitha, laith, lithum - mutato r in l et litteris
transpositis pro ilth ex alth, arth, attenuato a in i, sicut
in r. KIN germinare = जन्; hib. rith «course, flight,
gallop, race», rithim «I run, range, strull, rush».)
