कॢप्
2. कॢप् 10. P. कल्पयामि.
1) facere, efficere, creare.
RAGH. 8.46.: {#mama BAgyaviplavAd aSaniH kalpita
eza veDasA#}; R. Schl. I.35.1.: {#pOtrIm izwim
akalpayat#}; RAGH. 1.94.: {#kalpayAmAsa vanyAm
evA 'sya saMviDAm#} (Schol. Calc. = सम्पादयामास).
2) dare, impertire. RAM. I.53.10.: {#BAgAn na
