2) a name given to certain
days in the lunar month, as the full and change of the
moon and the 6th, 8th and 10th of each half month.
3) Particular periods of the year, as the equinox, solstice
etc.
4) the moment of the sun's entering a new sign.
5) a festival, a holiday.
6) Opportunity, occasion. MED.
7) a chapter, a book, the division of a work. OR. D.
8) a
moment, an instant SABD. CH. SA. 1.25. UR. 70.15.
