{#tO pArTivAnAm mizatAn narendra kfzRAm upAdAya
gatO narAgryO#}; 8159.: {#tvan Dakzyase 'naGa kARqavan
dAvam adyE 'va mizato 'sya SacIpateH#}; 2.2535.: {#DArtarAzwrAn
raRe hatvA mizatAM sarvaDanvinAm SamaN gantAsmi
na cirAt#}; 3.10464.: {#tena dvAdaSavArzikyAm
anAvfzwyAm mahAtmanA vfzwam…mizato vajrapARinaH#}.
(V. praef. उत् et नि et cf. मील्; russ. migaju et
mischu nictor; lith. mirkloju id., mếgmi dormio; fortasse
lat. nico, nic-to e nimic-0, nimic-to = निमिषामि. — Benfey
huc trahit lat. micare.)
c. उत् aperire oculos, proprie aufschlagen. BH. 5.9.:
उन्मिषन् निमिषन्न् अपि.
c. नि claudere oculos, proprie niederschlagen. MAH. 3.10649.:
मत्स्यः सुप्तो न निमिषति.
