oculis subjicere. SAK. 7.2.: रथवेगं रूपयति (v.
नट्); UR. 21.11.
c. नि
1) facere, perficere, peragere. MAN. 6.38.: {#nirUpye
'zwim#}.
2) percipere, videre, animadvertere. HIT. 23.3.:
छिद्रन् निरूप्य.
3) considerare, reputare, perpendere.
HIT. 10.3.: तन् निरूप्यताम्; 10.17.: {#tan nirUpayAmi
tAvat#}.
4) examinare, inquirere, explorare, investigare.
HIT. 20.15.: {#pakziBir itas tato nirUpayadBis
tarukoware SAvakAsTIni prAptAni#}; 90.1.: {#aham api
gatvA kim etad iti nirUpayAmi#}. Pervestigare,
perquirere, perscrutari. HIT. 68.14.: कोटरे निरूप्यमाणे.
5) eligere, ausersehen. HIT. 41.2.: {#awavIrAjye
'Bizektum BavAn…nirUpitaH#}.
c. वि (Denom. a विरूप deformis) deformare. HIT. 65.1.
R. Schl. I.1.44.
